title: Bank of England or Federal Reserve: Who will move first on interest rates?
text: Economics Bank of England or Federal Reserve: Who will move first on interest rates? Interest rate rises are on way for the first time since the financial crisis - what will it mean for either side of the Atlantic to go first? Central bank moves could send shockwaves through the currency markets Photo: SHAUN CURRY/AFP/Getty Images By Peter Spence , Economics Correspondent 1:36PM BST 01 Aug 2015
